{"title":"数据集整理","uid":"0f3682c753e2b6a31aa94d6bd3014bf2","slug":"数据集整理","date":"2022-04-08T11:59:16.000Z","updated":"2022-04-08T13:54:11.050Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/数据集整理.json","keywords":"Blog","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/background-7024520_1920.jpg"],"content":"<p>数据集汇总</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h1 id=\"CIFAR-10\"><a href=\"#CIFAR-10\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CIFAR - 10\"></a>CIFAR - 10</h1><p>   CIFAR-10是一个更接近普适物体的彩色图像数据集。CIFAR-10 是由Hinton 的学生Alex Krizhevsky 和Ilya Sutskever 整理的一个用于识别普适物体的<strong>小型数据集</strong>。一共包含<strong>10 个类别</strong>的RGB 彩色图片：飞机（ airplane ）、汽车（ automobile ）、鸟类（ bird ）、猫（ cat ）、鹿（ deer ）、狗（ dog ）、蛙类（ frog ）、马（ horse ）、船（ ship ）和卡车（ truck ）。<br>         每个图片的尺寸为32 × 32 ，每个类别有6000个图像，数据集中一共有50000 张训练图片和10000 张测试图片。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.cs.toronto.edu/~kriz/cifar.html\">CIFAR-10 and CIFAR-100 datasets (toronto.edu)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_41185868/article/details/82793025\">(1条消息) Dataset之CIFAR-10：CIFAR-10数据集简介、下载、使用方法之详细攻略_一个处女座的程序猿的博客-CSDN博客_cifar-10</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/90ce85b2faeb\">CIFAR10数据集手动下载和导入 - 简书 (jianshu.com)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/129081723\">CIFAR10数据集的下载及使用 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"数据集汇总 CIFA...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":524,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"人工智能","slug":"人工智能","count":6,"path":"api/categories/人工智能.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据集","slug":"数据集","count":1,"path":"api/tags/数据集.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CIFAR-10\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CIFAR - 10</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"https:/